                <h2>BEST APPLICATIONS</h2>
                <p>Flavor powders are perfect for dry mixes and are even used in some old-school baking applications. Flavor powders are good for:</p>
                <ul>
                  <li>Smoothies</li>
                  <li>Baked goods</li>
                  <li>Dry mixes</li>
                  <li>Maintaining a pre-made mix for months to come</li>
                </ul>
